3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper presents a control approach for a complex system, namely a parallel kinematic machine. 
4. cs.ME (Mechanical Engineering): The paper deals with the control of a mechanical system, namely the Orthoglide robot. 
5. cs.ROBOTS (Robotics): The paper proposes a control approach for a robot, which falls under the scope of this sub-category.
